Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.70,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Bloody pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.70,0:00:10.59,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You housebroken dogs in\Nyour sheltered environment,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.24,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,yappin' about "justice" when\Nyou know shit all about war...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.55,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I'll crush you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.37,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,That's why I've stayed alive\Nin this fucked-up world!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.44,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Should we retire for the time being?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I can keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.72,0:00:35.66,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Distracted as you are right now,\Nyou will not learn a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.64,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I shall now make my rounds through the forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,He saw straight through me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.02,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Good... memories...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Guess I'll head to the\NHarvest Festa for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.74,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Denied.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.54,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Aw, why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.01,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.87,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,I can't say I don't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.11,0:02:35.45,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,And here I thought I could go to a festival\Nwith friends for the first time...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Next year, for sure,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,let's go around the Harvest Festa\Nwith everyone from the occult club!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,With Shizuru and Prez, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.39,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,That sounds great.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.09,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah, really great!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.25,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It certainly does.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.89,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shizuru will be delighted, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.15,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.52,0:02:57.06,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'll have to drag my BFF, Yoshino, along with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,And of course, Kagari, you'll join us—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.41,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.16,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,She's been a bit quiet today, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.67,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.04,0:03:15.80,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kotori?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.55,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The barrier's been broken from the outside!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.93,0:03:31.83,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.69,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} here, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.92,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Is your little friend from Guardian here, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.32,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Or did she kick the bucket already?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.45,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You're the one who hurt Lucia!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.39,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I shoved a skewer through\Nher belly and barbecued her good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.08,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I grilled her just right, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.50,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.83,0:03:56.60,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Wow, you had a trick like that up your sleeve?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.09,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better show you my hand, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.34,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.97,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Bit of a waste to use it on shitters like you,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.47,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,but come on, have a little taste of {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.40,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Chibi-Moth! Everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.49,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Show them what you're made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.63,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You had a summoner kicking around, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.13,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What the heck is this monster?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.14,0:04:46.89,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.97,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.70,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Back from the grave I see, hunter.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.89,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,This time, I'll be sure to put you down for good.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.51,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Chibi-Moth, help us out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.16,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.11,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,We're running away!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.53,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be able to keep\Nthat daemon animated for long!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.53,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.66,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,This place is done for.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.97,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kotori.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.65,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,She's right! Let's run away, quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.42,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,That thing's bad news!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Easier said than done...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.30,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.02,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The trump cards are on their way.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.02,0:05:30.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.43,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,A gun?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.81,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Get 'em good, big guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.79,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Let's go, while we have the chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.04,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are Keisuke-san and Rikako-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.67,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are your parents here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.92,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.92,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.17,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kotori, listen to me—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.67,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,They're just daemons now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.18,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You ain't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.44,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of this complicated stuff,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.06,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,but I believe that we need to run for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.61,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,With this, we can protect our family.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.33,Default,Ri,0,0,0,,Yes. You are right, dear.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.20,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.90,Default,Ri,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let us go, dear.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.02,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.34,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.05,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's not possible...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.85,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{\an8}I mean, they're both already...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.72,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.72,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.30,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Get the {\i1}fuck{\i0} outta my way!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.48,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I should have known better\Nthan to extend myself so.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.65,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san, please be safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.75,Default,Ten,0,0,0,,We won't let you interfere with Midou!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.73,Default,Ten,0,0,0,,Gaia's Apex...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.96,Default,Ten,0,0,0,,Shall we see if you're truly as\Npowerful as the rumors say?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.36,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Kilimanjaro and Krivoy Rog?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.36,0:07:31.97,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I daresay they're a tad insufficient\Nto pit against me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.88,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,These damn small fry ate up my time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.52,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,We'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.45,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.29,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Bayern Knights of the Green Sword...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.92,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Move out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.03,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Guess I'm leaving now, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.03,0:08:11.05,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,But first, I would like to make something clear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.05,0:08:16.35,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,You and Lucia-chan aren't thinking\Nof doing anything stupid, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.20,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.56,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Good, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.61,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Well then, Shizuru-chan,\Nyou be a good girl and watch over the place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.11,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,You're our ace in the hole.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.53,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.46,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,You're a member of Guardian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.46,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,That day ten years ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.80,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The first daemons I created\Nafter becoming a druid
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.80,0:08:59.54,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,were my dad and mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.81,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,They could move and could even talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.31,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,But those were only reflexive\Nmovements from when they were alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.31,0:09:11.57,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,They were nothing but tools!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.39,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,And I just used them at my\Nconvenience, right to the very end...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.94,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I was with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,but I never noticed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.96,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I couldn't even remember the accident...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.96,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.45,0:09:35.97,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,There isn't a single thing you\Nneed to apologize to me for.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.91,0:09:37.97,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kotori?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are you all okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.94,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Yes! We're fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.22,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.65,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Go on without me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'll stop this guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.18,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.17,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.85,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You can't do it on your own!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.91,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.91,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'll definitely meet up with you later!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.89,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You'd better not be lying, okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.89,0:10:03.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.45,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Sacrificing yourself for others?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.04,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,How touching...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.00,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,It makes me wanna hurl!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I won't let you lay a finger on Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.38,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.72,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean the Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.26,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.10,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I'm sure hunters would go into a frenzy over that,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.43,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,but the one I'm here to kill is {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you so obsessed with me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.78,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,It ain't just you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.28,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You pieces of shit in this country
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.41,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,spend every day with your heads in the clouds,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.41,0:10:43.10,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,and it makes me wanna grind you all into dust!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.88,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Smarts, don't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.30,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,A peace-loving dumbass\Ncouldn't possibly endure this!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.28,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,He's getting destroyed!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.28,0:11:03.80,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,How is that man still alive with\Ntwo daemons that powerful in tow?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah, it hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.84,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,But, unfortunately for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.84,0:11:12.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,enduring pain is the one thing\Nthat jerk Sakuya instilled in me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.16,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You fuckin' brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.48,Default,Man,0,0,0,,"Bull's-eye!" as they say.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.32,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.49,Default,Man2,0,0,0,,I see. Talk about a real monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.19,Default,Noe,0,0,0,,The newbies would be no match for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.68,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Hunter reinforcements?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.11,0:11:44.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't me tell you're all...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.48,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Kiddo?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.15,0:11:52.85,Default,Man3,0,0,0,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.12,Default,Man3,0,0,0,,That's most likely the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.61,Default,Man3,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why we can see it, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.73,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.99,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,If we can see it, destroying it'll be a piece o' cake!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Like hell it will!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.12,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.34,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Take the Key and get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you helping us?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.00,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.14,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Why the hell did I make that stupid promise?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.64,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I'll burn you all to ashes, hunters!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.33,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,{\an8}L-Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.92,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.88,0:12:50.71,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,You're just doing whatever\Nthe hell you please, eh, Gaia?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.37,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Pot callin' the kettle black much, hunter?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.88,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Come on, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.12,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,The world always works this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.64,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,The weak have everything stolen from them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.64,0:13:15.94,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,That's why I'm gonna destroy it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.72,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.32,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,End of the line, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.14,Default,Yasu,0,0,0,,No, Midou.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.00,Default,Yasu,0,0,0,,You have to get along with everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.69,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,But he's such a total scatterbrain.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.38,Default,Yasu,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.64,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Damn, I wanted to see it so badly...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.37,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,To see this whole goddamn world
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.29,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,shatter to pieces...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.61,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.80,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,We allowed the Key to slip away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.80,0:14:28.14,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Also, that kid we decided to keep\Nan eye on was with the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.46,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.51,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Continue to pursue them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.31,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Tennouji, you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.03,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,If you let that thing live, it'll destroy the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.40,0:14:56.39,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Protect it with all you've got,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.04,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,and then fall into despair!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.19,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is the Salvation?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} the "you" you're looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.68,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Hey, keep it together!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.68,0:15:13.43,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,You're all battered and bruised!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.31,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Oh no, they caught up to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.06,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,Please stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.98,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.32,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I thought about it lots and lots.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.45,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if this is the right thing to do, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.23,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} a member of the occult club.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.19,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Shizu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Shizuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.84,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.28,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.73,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.48,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kotarou-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.23,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You woke up sooner than I expected, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.84,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You came for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.54,0:16:10.66,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Shizuru healed yours and Lucia's wounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.39,0:16:16.01,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We should be safe here for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.56,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What?! Where the heck are we?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.13,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,A Gaian facility called the\NCity of Stone, apparently.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.24,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.75,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Another world was created
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.84,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,on the flip side of our own via a Gaian technique,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.03,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,or something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.68,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,It's being used as a storage place for daemons.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.12,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I only vaguely remembered this place,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.35,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,but we managed to take refuge here somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,So, what about Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.26,0:16:44.35,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,She has been acting that way since this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.03,0:16:57.12,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Why are you so determined to destroy humanity?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.20,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,For generations,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.20,0:17:04.76,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,the saint's soul and memories have been\Ntransferred into our descendants.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.76,0:17:07.61,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You do not seem to have been consumed by it yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.86,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,but it has surely been engraved upon you already.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.86,0:17:14.44,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Because the saint lost hope in humans?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.44,0:17:19.14,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,With each successive generation,\Nour despair is sharpened and refined.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.14,0:17:24.89,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,We do not hold a single happy memory\Nwhich could make up for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.65,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,But I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.10,0:17:32.34,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You mean that farce at the school\Nwe sent you to on a whim?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.04,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Just try and fight it, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.37,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Try to fight the continuous chain\Nof despair which I pass to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.94,0:17:42.54,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,and you pass on to Shimako...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.93,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,The groundwork has been laid perfectly.\NThe time is right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.04,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,For this song to resonate throughout the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.64,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,we need to drag the Key\Nout into the world of the living.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.58,Default,Uku,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.96,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,After the Observer Tree appears,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.09,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,the choir will head for the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.33,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I'm about to head there myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.05,Default,Uku,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.68,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I will go, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.04,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.52,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.33,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Trunk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This sure takes me back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.46,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Now, if only {\i1}she{\i0} were here...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.73,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You mean Prez?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.67,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You've been way too quiet today!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.96,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Did you run out of feecof or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.39,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.34,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You actually have realized it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.71,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,This is the real Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.42,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,She isn't a living creature.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.14,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,She's simply a phenomenon
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.84,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,designed to cause the Salvation,\Ntaken human form.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.35,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,She's no different from a daemon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.87,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,But until just recently,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.87,0:18:48.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,she was saying whatever she wanted,\Ncausing people problems,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and getting all happy calling\Ncrappy coffee delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.02,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.28,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.19,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.25,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I couldn't find any.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Couldn't find what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.20,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Good memories involving mankind...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.63,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I couldn't find any.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.55,Default,Su,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Kashima?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.78,Default,Su,0,0,0,,You ordered all the summoners\Nto sortie into the city?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.55,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Are you trying to start a war?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.79,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.25,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I'm simply putting an end to everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.13,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.56,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.07,0:19:34.06,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,A fitting place to welcome the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.54,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're going to let the Key...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.54,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.05,Default,Su,0,0,0,,The Key should be nothing more\Nthan a tool to monitor destruction!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.07,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Who would actually wish\Nfor the world to truly end?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.66,Default,Su,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.09,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Those who know naught of true despair,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.09,0:20:00.63,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,who are merely discontent with life,\Nare nothing more than petty nuisances.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.94,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Now, Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.40,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Come forth.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.17,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.91,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What came over her all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.98,0:20:30.33,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,What is it, Chi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.78,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Um, don't you hear something?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.04,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.38,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Probably some sort of song...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.80,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That's right. This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.05,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The tree!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.11,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.43,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.42,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Did I underestimate the enemy a little too much?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.99,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I must return to Chihaya-san's side at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.17,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.76,0:21:23.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.69,Default,Person,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.70,Default,2,0,0,0,,That tree is...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.10,Default,3,0,0,0,,Huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.10,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey! What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.10,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,This is bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.36,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Is this Kazamatsuri?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:44.61,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Someone summoned all of us\Nfrom the City of Stone to Kazamatsuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.37,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Daemons, Kotarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.87,0:21:54.75,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.43,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,They're showing up in front of ordinary people?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.62,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.62,0:22:03.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.98,0:22:08.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The forest is spreading!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.61,0:22:18.31,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Has it begun?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.70,0:22:21.47,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,The time of Salvation is upon us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.78,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Humans...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.43,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,May your end be pleasant.
Comment: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.45,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}Little by little, the ripples drew apart from one another
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.45,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sukoshizutsu hamon wa hanarete itta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:15.21,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}And before we knew it, they no longer overlapped
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:15.21,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}itsu shika hitotsu mo kasanaranaku natta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:23.55,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}But it's okay as long as you're here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:23.55,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sore demo ii kimi to itara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.43,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}When did I start feeling this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.43,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}konna kimochi itsu kara idaita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:41.40,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}This is the love story of a certain boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:41.40,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}tada hitori no shounen no koimonogatari da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:47.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}To protect you till the end of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:47.62,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}eien ni kimi wo mamotte miseru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.91,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}I'll etch this upon my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.91,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}kono mune ni kizamikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:58.25,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}When did it start being just the two of us, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:58.25,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}itsu kara futarikiri ni natta n da kke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.88,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}But it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.88,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}mou ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:06.18,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}Just smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:06.18,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sonna koto waratte yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:12.18,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}On the eve of this world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:12.18,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}owaru sono hi ni wa
Comment: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 6,0:22:31.98,0:22:39.53,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}natsukashisa mo kieta yume
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.98,0:22:39.53,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Losing myself in a dream where even nostalgia lost form
Dialogue: 6,0:22:39.53,0:22:47.42,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}mayoi kono te ga samishiku kaze wo nadeta
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.53,0:22:47.42,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Lonely, I reached out with my hands to feel the wind's gentle caress
Dialogue: 6,0:22:47.42,0:22:54.46,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kotoba wo shiranai mama naraba
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.42,0:22:54.46,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}The names of those emotions still eluded me
Dialogue: 6,0:22:54.46,0:22:59.26,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kono hitomi wo tojiru koto mo
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.46,0:22:59.26,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Even closing my eyes for eternity
Dialogue: 6,0:22:59.26,0:23:03.93,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kantan datta no ni
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.26,0:23:03.93,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Should have been simple
Dialogue: 6,0:23:03.93,0:23:10.73,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}hajimete fureta nukumori
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.93,0:23:10.73,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}But I felt warmth for the first time
Dialogue: 6,0:23:10.73,0:23:16.19,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}chiisaku mebuku kodou ni
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.73,0:23:16.19,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}A tiny soul began to bud within my heart
Dialogue: 6,0:23:16.19,0:23:21.53,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}tomadoi wo oboeta
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.19,0:23:21.53,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}And I learned of bewilderment
Dialogue: 6,0:23:24.20,0:23:31.92,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}anata no koe sagashite mugen no michi wo yuku
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.20,0:23:31.92,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Walking on the path of eternity, searching for your voice
Dialogue: 6,0:23:31.92,0:23:39.63,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}hoshi no hajimari wo shiru tada sore dake
Dialogue: 5,0:23:31.92,0:23:39.63,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}I'm led to the time when stars are born, nothing more
Dialogue: 6,0:23:39.63,0:23:47.52,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kuchi ni nokoru nigami mo hiroku mada ki ni naru
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.63,0:23:47.52,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}This bitterness that lingers inside my mouth tempts my curiosity
Dialogue: 6,0:23:47.52,0:23:56.86,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}itsuka deau anata he saigo ni hohoemi wo
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.52,0:23:56.86,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}So I'll offer you one last smile before we meet again
